resource.name: Sales Tax Allocation, City-County Comparison Summary
resource.description: Sales tax allocation comparison summary reports present data on monthly local sales and use tax payments to local jurisdictions. These payments represent funds identified for local jurisdictions since the previous month’s distribution. When used with other local indicators, these reports may help indicate present and future economic trends. This table lists entities alphabetically by county name, then alphabetically by cities within the county.
